					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">One solution would be to have a rough area where an enemy should start. The area would be, say, 5x5 metatiles. Instead of having an exact location for the enemy, you would indicate the location of the area, and have the enemy start in a random non-solid tile within the area. This way you can still design screens with a general sense of where enemies will be when the player enters the screen.</div>

